-transformer des données
-avec le caractère '|'

<p>{{title | uppercase}}</p>

-à rajouter au app.module.ts 


*** pipes disponibles dans angular
-Lowercasepipe
    {{title | lowercase}}
-Uppercasepipe
    {{title | uppercase}}
-Datepipe
    {{todaydate | date:'d/M/y'}}
    {{todaydate | date:'shortTime'}}
-Currencypipe
    {{6589.23 | currency:"USD"}}
-Jsonpipe
    {{ jsonval | json }}
-Percentpipe
    {{00.54565 | percent}}
-Decimalpipe
    {{ 454.78787814 | number: '3.4-4' }}
-Slicepipe
    {{months | slice:2:6}}
-AsyncPipe
-I18nPluralPipe
-I18nSelectPipe
-KeyValuePipe
-TitleCasePipe 